{"tid":1453893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"召集今日搭車經過葵芳站巴絲","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:04:29.000Z","uid":136992,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72a3b26f1ee8b06f29a74543cdcf0d50549680c4","tid":1453893,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:37:59.000Z","msg":"記得拍卡入閘又好 行過又好 <br />\n然後去醫管局旗下診所或者醫院<br />\n瑪加列最近 不過好多藍醫 勇武唔好去<br />\n然後話自己今日行過葵芳站 之後呼吸唔舒服，皮膚過敏<br />\n要有大量市民 如果去完機場和你飛就經過葵芳站<br />\n大量市民不適 記者幫幫手 煲大地鐵站放催淚彈<br />\n推埋醫管局上台<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔舒服就要睇醫生"},{"pid":"f276b7c434107f3c1d35e404eabd54a8e047889a","tid":1453893,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:38:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"acd5b00bbca5ffa435a21a7f4e7a14e105813766","tid":1453893,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:39:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8e715656e9bdbc3461687df56587ad110099ffcb","tid":1453893,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:14.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"bb668aa9019ad770e4c0c51bbafc8d2866965881","tid":1453893,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"aaee78efd43fa3f787547b3e2a54bb30b5f8806d","tid":1453893,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"d345986b083428ee3add77003065b3747cd69c91","tid":1453893,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"d9e646fd29cc21e2a55c2fa078b30505e848dfa1","tid":1453893,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:56.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"0c4e7fbaf9afd3ec7dc19630bff6c4687435333e","tid":1453893,"uid":294822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:42:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ac1a8227cd3f7b948339867cfabcf2096e09e94","tid":1453893,"uid":1